text: The Qoros 5 is a compact Crossover SUV made by Qoros from 2016 to 2020. == History and Features == The Qoros 5 was debuted at the Guangzhou Auto Show in 2015. with sales starting in China in 2016 its the second car from the brand Qoros which is a joint venture between Kenon Holding and Chery the car has a 1.6 liter turbocharged petrol engine and both 6-speed manual and automatic transmission. == Markets == The Qoros 5 was sold only in the Chinese market. == Discontinuation == The production of the Qoros 5 ended in 2020 it was discontinued without sucessor. == References == Category:Sport utility vehicles Category:2010s automobiles Category:2020s automobiles Category:Chinese automobiles
